section.section:
The notices referred to in this subsection shall contain:
The museum's name, address, and telephone number;
A detailed description of the property;
The last known owner's name, if that information is available;
The last known owner's last known address, if that information is available;
A request that all persons who may have any knowledge of the whereabouts of the owner contact the museum and provide the information; and
A statement that if written assertion of title is not presented to the museum within six (6) months from the date of the final published notice, the title to the property shall vest in the museum, subject to KRS 171.843.
